{"tid":1301852,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果我係差人，肯定好憎Wave Sir呢類前線情緒失控嘅「手足」","createTime":"2019-07-09T17:52:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T13:09:28.000Z","uid":168267,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"54acbd3926848ac5ff8e3077f243ab913c872e75","tid":1301852,"uid":168267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T17:52:28.000Z","msg":"半夜三間，成大隊人馬要full gear、畀全香港人笑住咁去搣memo紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全因為有班智障嘅隊友，喺個唔關自己事嘅地方做咗，眾目睽睽之下做咗白痴嘢<br />\n<br />\n話就話「暴徒」，其實大家都心知肚明，如果示威嗰班人係唔啱，你咪跟足規矩用適當武力塔佢返去囉<br />\n偏偏係要扮好打得，連記者都郁埋，仲夠膽吹話唔使委任證架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前線班PK做得好好睇睇，咪唔會咁多位畀人入囉<br />\n累到成個警隊上下行親出街都畀人啤、反白眼，畀人笑冇學識<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過歸根究底，都係因為班高層落order叫人放心去做<br />\n上面梗係話你哋冇做錯到架啵<br />\n畀香港人笑白痴仔、食蛋、同啲新移民咸濕伯父一齊去撐警集會、守廁所護北姑呢啲你哋嚟做就梗啱架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecd350f92d68127682fc7abb54d0c7c17a08b1a8","tid":1301852,"uid":265192,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T17:53:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dmdqhY9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdmdqhY9.png&h=6636276f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d14fbca42b598431c518d83eaa4c3b6257319fa7","tid":1301852,"uid":168267,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ecd350f92d68127682fc7abb54d0c7c17a08b1a8","tid":1301852,"uid":265192,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T17:53:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dmdqhY9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdmdqhY9.png&h=6636276f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T17:54:29.000Z","msg":"咁快手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />設計得好靚"},{"pid":"c40ee916985c7bc573b237e85b6f45da548318ae","tid":1301852,"uid":34515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0